## 三、结构化数据（Schema.org）

### 3.1 Hub 页必须包含

```json
[BreadcrumbList, SoftwareApplication, FAQPage]
```

- `SoftwareApplication.name`：必须含年份
- `SoftwareApplication.dateModified`：= lastReviewed
- `SoftwareApplication.offers.price`：`"0"`
- `FAQPage.mainEntity`：必须与页面可见 FAQ 1:1 对应

### 3.2 Market 页必须包含

```json
[BreadcrumbList, SoftwareApplication, FAQPage]
```

- BreadcrumbList 必须 3 级：Home → Tool Hub → Market
- FAQPage 条目必须与 market-content.ts 中的 FAQ 完全一致
- 没有 FAQ 内容的市场不输出 FAQPage schema

### 3.3 验证红线

以下任一失败 = PR 不可合并：
- Schema 中的 FAQ 条目与页面可见 FAQ 数量不一致
- SoftwareApplication 缺少 dateModified
- BreadcrumbList URL 与 canonical 不同源

---

## 四、Metadata 模板

### 4.1 Hub 页

```
title: "{Platform} Pricing Calculator ({YEAR})"
description: "Free {platform} pricing calculator that back-solves the minimum listing price needed to reach your profit target. Accounts for {费用类型1}, {费用类型2}, {费用类型3}. Updated for {YEAR}. Last reviewed: {DATE}."
canonical: "/{slug}-pricing-calculator"
keywords: ["{platform} pricing calculator", "{platform} listing price calculator", ...]
```

### 4.2 Market 页

```
title: "{Platform} Pricing Calculator – {MarketFullName} ({YEAR})"
description: "Back-solve {platform} listing price for {MarketFullName}. Enter product cost, {平台特有输入}, and target profit to find the minimum profitable listing price after all {platform} fees. Updated for {YEAR}. Last reviewed: {DATE}."
canonical: "/{slug}-pricing-calculator/{marketId}"
```

### 4.3 Tier 3 市场追加

```
robots: { index: false, follow: true }
```

